title: Levi Strauss Signature Gold Women's Modern Skinny Jeans (Also Available in Plus)
description: Same great jeans, brand new name! Signature by Levi Strauss & Co. is now Levi Strauss Signature Gold
Super stretch lasts from day to night; Snug fit doesn't lose shape

Signature by Levi's strauss and co. Gold label modern skinny women's jeans offer quality craftsmanship and authentic style backed by over 160 years of denim heritage and expertise. Crafted from premium, super stretchy simply stretch denim that won't bag out and keeps its shape all day, our modern skinny jeans hug your curves for a perfect fit and are cut slim through the leg with a skinny leg opening for a long, lean look. Look and feel simply amazing in stylish and versatile simply stretch modern skinny jeans. Quality you trust from Levi's strauss and co., established 1853.
